<body>
  <div id="model"></div>

  <section id="index">
    <h1>原来孤独也是分等级的</h1>
    <p><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span></p>
    <div class="middle"> 
      <div class="imgs"><img src="../images/lonelytest/index_1.png" alt=""></div>
      <p>为什么一个人的时候感觉寂寞，人多了又好烦呢？</p>
      <div class="clears"></div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn">开始测试</button>
    <p class="follow">关注“小猪巴士”微信公众号，治疗孤独症！</p>
  </section>
  <section id="test" hidden>
    <div>
      <h2>今年的光棍节打算怎么过?</h2>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test1" checked><span><img src="../images/lonelytest/test11.jpg" alt=""></span></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test1"><span><img src="../images/lonelytest/test12.jpg" alt=""></span></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test1"><span><img src="../images/lonelytest/test13.jpg" alt=""></span></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test1"><span><img src="../images/lonelytest/test14.jpg" alt=""></span></label>
    </div>
    <div id="judge">
      <h2>你希望哪位网红是你的另一半？</h2>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test2" checked value="a3"><img src="../images/lonelytest/test21.jpg" alt=""></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test2" value="a5"><img src="../images/lonelytest/test22.jpg" alt=""></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test2" value="a8"><img src="../images/lonelytest/test23.jpg" alt=""></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test2" value="a1"><img src="../images/lonelytest/test24.jpg" alt=""></label>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>如果和男女神亲密接触，你想？</h2>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test3" checked><img src="../images/lonelytest/test31.jpg" alt=""></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test3"><img src="../images/lonelytest/test32.jpg" alt=""></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test3"><img src="../images/lonelytest/test33.jpg" alt=""></label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="test3"><img src="../images/lonelytest/test34.jpg" alt=""></label>
    </div>
    <button class="btn">查看结果</button>
    <p class="follow">关注“小猪巴士”微信公众号，治疗孤独症！</p>
  </section>
  <section id="result" hidden>
    <h3><span id ="user-name">${nickname}</span>的鉴定结果为：</h3>
    <p class="al-title"></p>
    <button class="share btn">点击分享</button>
    <div class="middle">
      <p class="al-desc1"></p>
      <div class="als">
      	<p class="al-desc2"></p>
      	<div class="clears"></div>
      	<div class="imgs"><img src="../images/lonelytest/result_1.png" alt=""></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="follow">关注“小猪巴士”微信公众号，治疗孤独症！</p>
  </section>

  <div id="share-layout">
    <div class="imgs"><img src="../images/lonelytest/share.png" alt=""></div>
    <button class="iknow btn">已阅</button>
  </div>
 
